"These are the catalogs used for the loaded plate solved image:\n"
"\n"
"- Automatic: Uses local catalogs if available, otherwise defaults to nomad.\n"
"\n"
"You can also choose an alternate online catalog:\n"
"\n"
"- for stars: tycho2, nomad, gaia, ppmxl, bsc, apass, gcvs, vsx, simbad, "
"aavso_chart\n"
"- for exoplanets: exo\n"
"- for deep-sky: pgc\n"
"- for solar system objects: solsys (closest IAU observatory code can be "
