#: src/gui/uifiles/siril.ui:1990
msgid ""
"Create synthetic Gaussian / Moffat star mask with perfect profiles for every "
"star detected by Siril's star finder routine, using parameters measured from "
"the original data. The star mask can be recombined with a starless image to "
"fix aberrations.\n"
"Star synthesis should be applied <i>before</i> <b>stretching</b>.\n"
"Star selection can be manually fine-tuned using the Dynamic PSF tool."
msgstr ""
"Crie uma máscara estelar sintética Gaussiana/Moffat com perfis perfeitos "
"para cada estrela detectada pela rotina de busca de estrelas do Siril, "
"usando parâmetros medidos a partir dos dados originais. A máscara estelar "
